            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div property="schema:text"><p>Pearl Abyss has revealed the specifications for its upcoming open-world RPG Crimson Desert. Whether you plan to play the game on PC, console, Mac, or even the Xbox ROG Ally, you’ll now know exactly how powerful your machine needs to be when the game launches next week on March 19.&nbsp;</p><hr>



