<h3>PlayStation 5</h3><h4><u>Resolution</u></h4><p><strong>Performance: </strong>1080p<br><strong>Balanced:</strong> Upscaled 4K (from 1280p, FSR 3)<br><strong>Quality:</strong> Upscaled 4K (from 1440p, FSR 3)</p><h4><u>Target Performance</u></h4><p><strong>Performance:</strong> 60 FPS Vsync/60+ FPS VRR<br><strong>Balanced: </strong>40 FPS Vsync<br><strong>Quality:</strong> 30 FPS Vsync</p><h4><u>Raytracing Quality</u></h4><p><strong>Performance:</strong> Raytracing Low<br><strong>Balanced:</strong> Raytracing Low<br><strong>Quality:</strong> Raytracing High</p><h3>PlayStation 5 Pro</h3><h4><u>Resolution</u></h4><p><strong>Performance:</strong> Upscaled 4K (from 1080p, Upgraded PSSR)<br><strong>Balanced:</strong> Upscaled 4K (from 1440p, Upgraded PSSR)<br><strong>Quality:</strong> 4K&nbsp;</p><h4><u>Target Performance</u></h4><p><strong>Performance:</strong> 60 FPS Vsync/60+ FPS VRR<br><strong>Balanced:</strong> 40 FPS Vsync/48+ FPS VRR<br><strong>Quality:</strong> 30 FPS Vsync</p><h4><u>Raytracing Quality</u></h4><p><strong>Performance:</strong> Raytracing High<br><strong>Balanced:</strong> Raytracing High<br><strong>Quality:</strong> Raytracing Ultra</p><h3>Xbox Series S</h3><h4><u>Resolution</u></h4><p><strong>Performance:</strong> 720p<br><strong>Quality:</strong> 1080p</p><p><u>Target Performance</u><br><strong>Performance:</strong> 40 FPS Vsync<br><strong>Quality:</strong> 30 FPS Vsync</p><p><u>Raytracing Quality</u><br><strong>Performance:</strong> Raytracing Off<br><strong>Quality:</strong> Raytracing Off</p><h4>Xbox Series X/S</h4><h4><u>Resolution</u></h4><p><strong>Performance:</strong> 1080p<br><strong>Balanced:</strong> Upscaled 4K (from 1280p, FSR 3)<br><strong>Quality:</strong> Upscaled 4K (from 1440p, FSR 3)</p><h4><u>Target Performance</u></h4><p><strong>Performance:</strong> 60 FPS Vsync/60+ FPS VRR<br><strong>Balanced:</strong> 40 FPS Vsync<br><strong>Quality:</strong> 30 FPS Vsync</p><h4><u>Raytracing Quality</u></h4><p><strong>Performance:</strong> Raytracing Low<br><strong>Balanced:</strong> Raytracing Low<br><strong>Quality:</strong> Raytracing High</p><hr><h2>ROG Xbox Ally Specs</h2>



