<h3>ROG Xbox Ally</h3><h4><u>Resolution</u></h4><p><strong>Performance:</strong> 720p (FSR 3 Frame Generation)</p><h4><u>Target Performance</u></h4><p><strong>Performance:</strong> 40 FPS</p><h4><u>Storage</u></h4><p>150 GB</p><h3>ROG Xbox Ally X</h3><h4><u>Resolution</u></h4><p><strong>Performance:</strong> Upscaled 1080p (from 720p, FSR 3 Super Resolution/Frame Generation)<br><strong>Balanced:</strong> Upscaled 1080p (from 720p, FSR 3 Super Resolution)<br><strong>Quality:</strong> 1080p</p><h4><u>Target Performance</u></h4><p><strong>Performance:</strong> 60 FPS<br><strong>Balanced:</strong> 40 FPS<br><strong>Quality:</strong> 30 FPS</p><h4><u>Storage</u></h4><p>150 GB</p><hr><h2>Mac Specs</h2>



