<h4><u>Performance Specs (MacOS 15/MetalFX Upscale)</u></h4><p><strong>Minimum: </strong>720p - 30 FPS/900p - 30 FPS<br><strong>Recommended:</strong> 1080p - 30 FPS<br><strong>High:</strong> 1440p - 30 FPS<br><strong>Ultra: </strong>4K - 40 FPS</p><h4><u>Performance Specs (MacOS 26+/MetalFX Upscale/Frame Interpolation)</u></h4><p><strong>Minimum:</strong> 720p - 60 FPS/900p - 60 FPS<br><strong>Recommended: </strong>1080p - 60 FPS<br><strong>High:</strong> 1440p - 60 FPS<br><strong>Ultra:</strong> 4K - 60 FPS</p><h4><u>MacOS</u></h4><p><strong>All:</strong> 15.0 or later</p><h4><u>Chip</u></h4><p><strong>Minimum:</strong> M2 Pro, M3,M4<br><strong>Recommended:</strong> M3 Pro, M4 Pro, M5<br><strong>High:</strong> M2 Max/M3 Max<br><strong>Ultra:</strong> M3 Ultra, M4 Max</p><h4><u>Raytracing</u></h4><p><strong>Minimum:</strong> Off (M2 Pro)/On (M3, M4)<br><strong>Recommended:</strong> On (M3 Pro, M4 Pro, M5)<br><strong>High:</strong> Off (M2 Max)/On (M3 Max)<br><strong>Ultra:</strong> On (M3 Ultra, M4 Max)</p><h4><u>RAM</u></h4><p><strong>All:</strong> 16 GB</p><h4><u>Storage (Steam)</u></h4><p><strong>All:</strong> 150 GB</p><h4><u>Storage (App Store)</u></h4><p><strong>All:</strong> 150 GB</p><hr><p>Crimson Desert will be available on March 19 for PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X/S, PC, and Mac.&nbsp;</p></div></div><br/><br/>https://gameinformer.com/2026/03/10/crimson-desert-specs-for-pc-console-and-other-platforms-revealed]]></content:encoded>
